WEBVTT

00:03.117 --> 00:05.435
Did you have a good time last weekend?

00:06.871 --> 00:07.797
Yes, I did.

00:09.245 --> 00:10.548
What did you do?

00:11.619 --> 00:13.421
I went hiking with my dad.

00:14.629 --> 00:15.735
So did I.

00:18.205 --> 00:20.146
You don't look happy. What's wrong?

00:21.180 --> 00:23.986
I was going to visit my grandma yesterday.

00:24.419 --> 00:26.987
I made special cookies for my grandma.

00:28.415 --> 00:30.198
Wow. That's very nice!

00:31.538 --> 00:34.902
But I couldn't visit her because it rained heavily.

00:36.505 --> 00:37.749
That's too bad.

